<view>
  <view> 生辰八字查询 </view>
  <view bindtap="datetimePickClick"> 请选择出生日期/时刻 </view>
  <view bindtap="datetimePickClick" class="yh-nostyle-input"> {{currentDateStr}} </view>
  <van-popup show="{{ showDatetimePick }}" position="top" custom-style="height: 100%;">
    <van-datetime-picker
      type="datetime"
      value="{{ currentDate }}"
      formatter="{{ formatter }}"
      bind:confirm="datetimePickConfirm"
      bind:cancel="datetimePickCancel"
    />
  </van-popup>

  <van-button plain type="primary" bindtap="calc">查看八字</van-button>
  <view wx:if="{{showCaclResult}}">
    <van-cell-group>
      <van-cell title="阳历：" title-width="15%" value="{{moment.solar}}" />
      <van-cell title="阴历：" title-width="15%" value="{{moment.lunar}}" />
      <van-cell title="生肖：" title-width="15%" bindtap="onclickSx">
        <text class="yh-nostyle-tip">{{moment.shengxiao}} </text> <view/>
        <text wx:if="{{showSxLuck}}" class="yh-nostyle-tip2">宜：{{sxLuck.good}}</text>
        <text wx:if="{{showSxLuck}}" class="yh-nostyle-tip2">忌：{{sxLuck.bad}}</text>
      </van-cell>
      <van-cell title="八字：" title-width="15%" value="{{moment.bazi}}" />
      <van-cell title="五行：" title-width="15%" bindtap="onclick5X">
        <text class="yh-nostyle-tip">{{moment.wuxing}} </text> <view/>
        <text wx:if="{{show5XXsXk}}" class="yh-nostyle-tip2">附：五行相生相克关系表</text>
        <text wx:if="{{show5XXsXk}}" class="yh-nostyle-tip2">相生：木生火/火生土/土生金/金生水/水生木。</text>
        <text wx:if="{{show5XXsXk}}" class="yh-nostyle-tip2">相克：水克火/火克金/金克木/木克土/土克水。</text>
      </van-cell>
      <van-cell title="喜用：" title-width="15%">
        <text bindtap="onclickXy" class="yh-nostyle-tip">{{moment.xiyong}}</text>
       </van-cell>
       <van-cell title-width="0%" wx:if="{{showXiyongTip}}">
        <text>喜用神的计算是基于日柱天干同类五行和异类五行的平衡。一般是缺补旺抑。
        同类五行：指日柱天干的五行，加上其的相生五行。
        比如日柱天干是“木”的话，水生木，木和水是同类五行，另外三个是异类五行。
        同类五行能量强于异类五行，则是常说的生辰八字偏旺，相反则是偏弱。
        八字旺，分为正常旺以及特殊格局，如果是正常旺，用“旺则抑，弱则扶”原理即可。
        如果是特殊的旺，比如日柱天干5以上这种，无法抑制，只能顺从。
        </text>
      </van-cell>
    </van-cell-group>
  </view>



  <view>
    <view class="yh-nostyle-title2">最新推出：以天为单位查询 ( ↓↓↓ )</view>
  </view>

  <view bindtap="dayPickClick">请选择出生日期</view>
  <view bindtap="dayPickClick" class="yh-nostyle-input">{{currentDayStr}}</view>
  <van-popup show="{{ showDayPick }}" position="top" custom-style="height: 100%;">
    <van-datetime-picker
      type="date"
      value="{{ currentDay }}"
      formatter="{{ formatter }}"
      bind:confirm="dayPickConfirm"
      bind:cancel="dayPickCancel"
    />
  </van-popup>
  <van-button plain type="primary" bindtap="calc_oneday_show">查看全天</van-button>

  <view wx:if="{{showAllDay}}">
    <view class="panel-body">
      <view><label>阳历：{{daySolar}}</label></view>
      <view><label>阴历：{{dayLunar}}</label></view>
      <view wx:for="{{dayItems}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="hour">
        <view class="yh-nostyle-tip">{{item.hour}}</view>
        <view> 八字： {{item.bazi}}</view>
        <view> 五行： {{item.wuxing}}</view>
        <view> {{item.xiyong}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

</view>